Description: CVE-2026-61870 - Fix memory leak in ImageMagick VIFF encoder
 In WriteVIFFImage (coders/viff.c), when the VIFF colormap allocation via
 AcquireQuantumMemory fails, the code threw MemoryAllocationFailed without
 first relinquishing the previously-allocated pixel_info virtual memory,
 leaking it (CWE-401). Release pixel_info before throwing the exception.
Origin: upstream, commit:fdbf39ba9a681e53e6025d40501ae5a2bfec300
Author: Cristy <urban-warrior@imagemagick.org>
Last-Update: 2026-07-14

--- a/coders/viff.c
+++ b/coders/viff.c
@@ -1146,7 +1146,10 @@ static MagickBooleanType WriteVIFFImage(const ImageInfo *image_info,
           viff_colormap=(unsigned char *) AcquireQuantumMemory(image->colors,
             3*sizeof(*viff_colormap));
           if (viff_colormap == (unsigned char *) NULL)
-            ThrowWriterException(ResourceLimitError,"MemoryAllocationFailed");
+            {
+              pixel_info=RelinquishVirtualMemory(pixel_info);
+              ThrowWriterException(ResourceLimitError,"MemoryAllocationFailed");
+            }
           q=viff_colormap;
           for (i=0; i < (ssize_t) image->colors; i++)
             *q++=ScaleQuantumToChar(ClampToQuantum(image->colormap[i].red));
Description: Fix CVE-2026-61866 memory leak in WriteOneJNGImage (JNG encoder)
 The JNG encoder (WriteOneJNGImage in coders/png.c) leaks the allocated
 jpeg_image_info and jpeg_image structures when the status check after
 OpenBlob() fails, because it throws the writer exception without freeing
 them first. An attacker can trigger repeated resource exhaustion via
 crafted/malformed JNG conversions (CWE-401).
 .
 This backports the upstream fix to destroy jpeg_image_info and jpeg_image
 before throwing the ResourceLimitError exception on the failed status
 check. Only the security-relevant hunk is applied; the upstream commit's
 second hunk simplifies a blob-null-check cleanup path that does not exist
 in this 7.1.1-43 source tree.
Origin: upstream, commit:0bb3578ee087f3c4f14bbf1d8883ae456fc99092
Author: Cristy <urban-warrior@imagemagick.org>
Last-Update: 2026-07-16
---
--- a/coders/png.c
+++ b/coders/png.c
@@ -12705,7 +12705,11 @@
       (double) jpeg_image->rows);

   if (status == MagickFalse)
-    ThrowWriterException(ResourceLimitError,"MemoryAllocationFailed");
+    {
+      jpeg_image_info=DestroyImageInfo(jpeg_image_info);
+      jpeg_image=DestroyImage(jpeg_image);
+      ThrowWriterException(ResourceLimitError,"MemoryAllocationFailed");
+    }

   if (jng_color_type == 8 || jng_color_type == 12)
     jpeg_image_info->type=GrayscaleType;
